room_title: Escape room "Escape an 80's Dance Party" by Great Room Escape in Cincinnati
room_address: 4814 Peter Pl, West Chester Township, OH 45246
room_description: Grab your Aqua Net, lace up your high tops, and moonwalk back in time! It’s 1980 something and tonight you and your gnarly team of super freaks have made the VIP list to the party of the century. You’ll need to complete the challenges, solve the riddles and beat the DJ on the dance floor before you find yourselves Trapped in the 80’s FOREVER!
